<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.2/css/all.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400,500,700&display=swap">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mdbootstrap/4.18.0/css/mdb.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.4/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mdbootstrap/4.18.0/js/mdb.min.js"></script>
  <script src="//cdn.datatables.net/1.10.21/js/jquery.dataTables.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="//cdn.datatables.net/1.10.21/css/jquery.dataTables.min.css">
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/sweetalert/dist/sweetalert.min.js"></script>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/main.css">
  <title>장곡중 발열체크</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="loading">
    <div class="jumbotron text-center">
      <div class="spinner-grow text-info" role="status"></div>
      <br />
      <h4>
        서버에서 정보를 가지고 오고 있습니다<br />
        잠시만 기다려 주세요...
      </h4>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="status row text-center">
      <div class="col-lg-3 text-white text-center hvr-icon-up status-item status-all">
          <h1><i class="fas fa-users"></i></h1>
          <h5 class="card-title">전채 사용자 수</h5>
          <h6 class="card-title">
            <%= data.length %>명 등록됨
          </h6>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 text-white text-center hvr-icon-up status-item status-need">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-user-times"></i></h1>
        <h5 class="card-title">검사가 필요한 사용자 수</h5>
        <h6 class="card-title">
          <%= data.filter((d) => !d.checked).length %>명 필요
        </h6>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 text-white text-center hvr-icon-up status-item status-complete">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-user-check"></i></h1>
        <h5 class="card-title">검사가 완료된 사용자 수</h5>
        <h6 class="card-title">
          <%= data.filter((d) => d.checked).length %>명 완료
        </h6>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 text-white text-center hvr-icon-up status-item status-percent">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-user-cog"></i></h1>
        <h5 class="card-title">검사 비율</h5>
        <h6 class="card-title">
          검사필요: <%= Math.round(data.filter((d) => !d.checked).length / data.length * 100) %>% /
          검사완료: <%= Math.round(data.filter((d) => d.checked).length / data.length * 100) %>%
        </h6>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card progress-card">
      <div class="card-body progress-card-body">
        <% const grade0 = Math.round(data.filter((d) => d.grade === 0 && d.checked).length / data.length * 100) %>
        <% const grade1 = Math.round(data.filter((d) => d.grade === 1 && d.checked).length / data.length * 100) %>
        <% const grade2 = Math.round(data.filter((d) => d.grade === 2 && d.checked).length / data.length * 100) %>
        <% const grade3 = Math.round(data.filter((d) => d.grade === 3 && d.checked).length / data.length * 100) %>

        <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar bg-secondary" role="progressbar" style="color: white; width: <%= grade0 %>%"><%= grade0 %>%</div>
          <div class="progress-bar bg-success" role="progressbar" style="color: white; width: <%= grade1 %>%"><%= grade1 %>%</div>
          <div class="progress-bar bg-danger" role="progressbar" style="color: white; width: <%= grade2 %>%"><%= grade2 %>%</div>
          <div class="progress-bar bg-warning" role="progressbar" style="color: white; width: <%= grade3 %>%"><%= grade3 %>%</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="Basic example">
      <button type="button" class="ml-0 mt-0 btn btn-info" onclick="add()">사용자추가</button>
      <button type="button" class="mt-0 btn btn-danger" onclick="reset()">체크 초기화</button>
      <button type="button" class="mt-0 btn btn-warning" onclick="window.location.reload()">새로고침</button>
    </div>

    <table id="table" class="table table-striped table-bordered table-sm">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="th-sm">바코드 ID</th>
          <th class="th-sm">학년/반/번호</th>
          <th class="th-sm">이름</th>
          <th class="th-sm">체크여부</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
      </tbody>
    </table>

      <div class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissible fade show mt-1" role="alert">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
        웹페이지에 문제가 발생하면 "3-3 박민혁"을 불러주세요 (맞춤법/오타 지적은 환영입니다)<br />
        이 웹 페이지에서 해결할 수 없는 문제(정보오류)가 발생하면 "3-3 박민혁 혹은 3-4 임태현, 배재현"을 불러주세요
      </div>
      <div class="alert alert-info alert-dismissible fade show mt-1" role="alert">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
        모든 저작권은 (칠곡) 장곡중학교와 Software And Guiders(SWAG, 장곡중 소프트웨어 동아리)에 있으며, 무단 복제 및 2차 배포를 금합니다<br />
        일부 디자인은 트위터에서 제작한 Bootstrap을 사용하였습니다 (MIT License), 또한 전자정부 프레임워크를 참고하여 제작되었습니다
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/src/main.js"></script>
  </body>
  </html>